title: Miss Spiders Sunny Patch Friends - A Cloudy Day in Sunny Patch
description:
Miss Spider's Sunny Patch Friends A Cloudy Day in Sunny patch


Gentle Miss Spider, quite possibly the world's only vegan insect, tries to teach her many children, including Shimmer, Dragon, Bounce, Squirt, Spinner, Snowdrop and Pansy, about life and getting along with others. Based on the series of children's books by David Kirk.

Episodes :  A Cloudy Day in Sunny Patch / Eight is Not Enough / Something's Stinky in Sunny Patch / Star Fell on Sunny Patch / Ground House Rules 

tv rip 58 min long
